      "id": "tutorial-production-mode-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.555418,
      "replayEndSec": 11.051619,
      "narrationText": "让我们从笔记本以生产模式启动应用。部署命令调用了我们开发时使用的同一个 up 函数，但以脱离方式运行。你可以关上笔记本，应用依然持续运行。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-01.3567ea89.mp3",
      "textHash": "3567ea89a095afdebdf73da735759ad83005f44fe06fe04461fc6fbf3991bf0f",
      "audioDurationSec": 14.759184,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-01-after.351f749b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 8.594286,
      "afterTextHash": "351f749b1039115df03e4379e9c479e0f31265a46a25ef085c91199d43895277"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-production-mode-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 11.051619,
      "replayEndSec": 18.718543,
      "narrationText": "让我们启用自动启动，确保应用在服务器重启后能自动恢复。从现在起，只要服务器重启，这个仓库就会自动启动。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-02.04b0be7c.mp3",
      "textHash": "04b0be7c3f3d37984a99f9085fa899b725c2bfd009114adf2ad1301bf377f91c",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.997551,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-02-after.aa10e80b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.63102,
      "afterTextHash": "aa10e80b6787546a921dffc581127bde752fdb44dd066a89302ff7f681b34b62"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-production-mode-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 18.718543,
      "replayEndSec": 25.169818,
      "narrationText": "让我们列出哪些仓库已启用自动启动，确认我们的应用已加入启动列表。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-03.bb0f19a3.mp3",
      "textHash": "bb0f19a3dfe19424ece93f2e88da8130ad4e2045aeb5ce8eb506fb19ee22e73e",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.269388,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-03-after.4c1d9786.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.272653,
      "afterTextHash": "4c1d9786deebe51d8f4711cbb49413bece7919169334c1b27a7d60876c655217"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-production-mode-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 25.169818,
      "replayEndSec": 31.824598,
      "narrationText": "停止应用时，从笔记本发出一条命令即可。一条命令启动，一条命令停止，全从终端完成，不再需要交互式连接。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-04.8707a2d0.mp3",
      "textHash": "8707a2d08c6429854053b1a3c5c716058b28919651f97aa619fa1e03e9010493",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.795918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/tutorial-production-mode-04-after.489bb141.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.586122,
      "afterTextHash": "489bb141e1fb09f7f3d61fef5cb1e5db5c6f41958cc243d5ed60a4d84e9925e1"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "6ec166226629af86b9b0e8c9c0d9b74cd36a72b64981222c56c0cfc9b942e408",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/intro.6ec16622.mp3",
      "narrationText": "你连着的时候，应用就在跑。生产环境的意思是，你断开之后它也继续跑。三个简单步骤，全在你的笔记本上完成。",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.684082
    },
    {
      "id": "dev-vs-prod",
      "textHash": "554edc726ce0c4440970473f64534caf71c41375139db316a452db7037cc5c80",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-production-mode/dev-vs-prod.554edc72.mp3",
      "narrationText": "区别就在这里。开发环境下，你通过 SSH 在 repo 内部启动应用。会话一关，应用也跟着停掉。生产环境下，启动时与你的笔记本分离，服务器持有进程，跟你的连接无关。",
      "audioDurationSec": 25.547755
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "textHash": "eeb3bd0e4abab390be28f73907e4799847abbaaf009805362892377c4f3fd6a3",
